latestPosts.caption:
A magical moment.✨🧿
As we hold this gold play button celebrating our family of 1M on YouTube, we reflect upon our journey. A journey filled with more lows than highs, more downs than ups, yet absolutely worth it. Why? Because of all you beautiful people. Words fall short to express our gratitude for all the unconditional love & support we receive from our #FunyaasiFam. Thank you for including us in your lives, for being a part of our community, for giving us your time & for pushing us when times were hard. As for the two of us, we always used to wonder how it would feel like to hold this button, and it feels unreal. We have learned that hard work and consistency will always pay off. Always! So to anyone who’s hustling for their dreams, just keep at it. 🤜🏻
As we always say, we’re on a mission to spread to smiles, and a milestone like this, is reassuring that we’re on the right path. 
A huge shoutout to our families & friends for trusting us and having faith in our work. 

Love you all. ❤️

Also thanks to @youtube @youtubeindia for providing us with a platform to bring out our ideas to life & for sending this beauty you see in our hands.

#funyaasi #funyaasifam #goldplaybutton #milestone

latestPosts.caption:
What an incredible weekend celebrating the 25 unforgettable years of IIFA Awards! ✨

IIFA has always been a core childhood memory for us. Watching the show on TV every year, we used to wonder, “LIVE dekhne mein kya mazaa aata hoga yaar”. 

If someone would have told Little Shubham and Dhruv that few years down the line, they’ll be attending the show, walking the green carpet, celebrating & witnessing the magic and grandeur of Indian cinema and culture, unko vishwaas he na hota. But here we are, making them proud.

So grateful that we got it be in a room full of icons and legends who we have looked up to all our lives - watching their stellar performances on stage and screaming our lungs out in disbelief! (SHAHRUKHHHHH! AAAAAH!) Will take some time to get over it. 🧿

Too much to share but right now the only thing we can say is ‘Thank You’. Dil se thank you to our lovely Funyaasi Fam for supporting us in this journey and making our dreams come true. Also, thanks to @metaindia for this amazing opportunity!

Ab hum ja rahe hain saari photos aur videos ghar walon ko dikhaane 😂❤️

Styled by @styledbymannat
